703938f-a.title: Brooklyn: Dean Street - Ralph Avenue
703938f-a.text:
Dean Street, east from Ralph Avenue. On the north side (left)
of the street, and extending to Howard Avenue, is Brooklyn Hebrew
gOrphan Asylum.
View 2 shows the Ralph Avenue side of the orphan asylum.
July 13, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
NO REEPRODUCTIONS
Dean St. east from Ralph Ave.
Aug. 2, 1941
P.L. Sperr
Neg. A-231
